Germany’s Opposition to Block Tax Cuts, Welt am Sonntag Reports

-- B y   R i c h a r d   W e i s s
-- 
2011-06-25T12:38:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-25/germany-s-opposition-to-block-tax-cuts-welt-am-sonntag-reports.html
Tax cuts planned by German
Chancellor  Angela Merkel  are a violation of the country’s
constitution and the opposition  Social Democratic Party  will
block them in the upper house, or Bundesrat,  Welt am Sonntag 
reported, citing  Sigmar Gabriel , national chairman of the
opposition party.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Richard Weiss in Frankfurt at 
 rweiss5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at   bkammel@bloomberg.net  